Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我的幻觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阿斯多利亚的都城”帕拉斯”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见到了蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那家伙则与他的哥哥再次碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我见到他遭到攻击的那个不祥影像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实尚未结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是帕拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满着海洋气息的美丽都市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手居然是个小鬼,这工作还真轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说好了,先砍到他的人\N可以拿走一半奖金,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来今晚可以暍到好酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有预期的别离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然只破坏了能源石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本就不算比试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…卑鄙了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不认为三对一有违骑士之道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡扯什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是代表本王对伊斯帕农制人型装甲的敬意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾在实际战斗中同时迎战过更多的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是武艺高强的法尼利亚王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话说得真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪寨巴哈那么想得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架装甲可以卖到很好的价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始估价了.真像你的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼真是一架优异的人型装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它美到越看它越觉得心动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,论起美貌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它还是比不上蜜拉娜公主与艾莉丝公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅甸大人,你真会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启禀阿斯顿王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为它的美貌这个消息可能会传到寨巴哈那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该怎么办才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让艾斯嘉科尼假扮成我国的人型装甲如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要藏木头的话还是森林最恰当.是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厂房那边已经做好准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼利亚王,您意下如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就交由您决定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过于美丽也是一种罪恶吧,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫小瞳是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你是亚连大人带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的故乡在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是从相当不可思议的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是个有着不可思议的\N风土民情的遥远国度来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好暍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然将维农酒一□气暍完的确异于常人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否请您告知详情,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主,这种话题并不适合这个场合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,这句话是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也不过是个侍女罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没陪我一同去逛市集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到我一切安顿妥当之后必定奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了喔,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,蜜拉娜和梅甸大人的长男订婚了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你想跟他说的不是这件事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是天大的好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜您,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有答应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父王擅自…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了你的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说我们已经好多年都没见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从他上了商船之后就没回来家里过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过与蜜拉娜公主的大喜之日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定得叫他回来露个脸才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来亚连还有机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢等待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经清楚龙的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用着急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点把龙抓起来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样多伦卡喀大人一定也会龙心大悦的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是亚德罗福斯将军大人传来的信函
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚德罗福斯大人传来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下达进攻弗雷特指令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等将领军前往阿斯多利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四将军亲自领军?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他们找到能源点了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说多伦卡喀大人一直在寻找的东西终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运预测装置已探得龙影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顷于作战开始前捕获
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附记
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别兴奋过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上为信函内容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要攻下弗雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军就必须以这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是以阿斯多利亚港为中继站
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是不准你轻率行动\N引起阿斯多利亚的反感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区港□占领下来不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:09:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是想要还他这笔债罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要报仇等抓到人之后也不迟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真愿意把他交给我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你弟弟被抓到的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个连祖国都能毁灭的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从寨巴哈的留驻军书信来看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像已经感觉到了艾斯嘉科尼就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等他们知道再给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做也不会有损于我国的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能知道他们为什么如此关注这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能牵他们的鼻子走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连带回来的那个奇怪的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个喜欢珍奇事物的梅甸也好像很关注她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个侍女?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有密报说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是来自幻之月的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能就是哪里乡下的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主,有事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再继续诱惑蜜拉娜了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道蜜拉娜深深被你所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却只是将她当成是玛莲妮王姊的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜越来越像王姊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会那么看她或许也是莫可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但蜜拉娜终究不是王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望看到蜜拉娜伤心难过的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后难过的总是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再谈恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来当你的对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼神之牌三张
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从朋友到恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:11:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LA RUOTA 命运之轮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状况的急变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,真是好牌都聚集在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只笨猫!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!好热!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短期间内有着如此的进步着实令人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的招式完全不重视防御
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去,他迟早…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会出事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好精彩的剑术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间并不适合淑女外出散步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,但也不适合练剑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有婚约在身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做并不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是父王擅自决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么就是不肯接受我的心意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也暍多了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劝你还是别上去的好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得好热
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要上去吹吹风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只肯喊我"公主"呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个爱上你的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以为了你抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是父王还是这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连会有心上人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是理所当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才刚认识没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的夜景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼利亚的夜晚也很美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片星光闪闪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?难道你在哭吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来管我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的在哭耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要哭?告诉我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭死你算了.哼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女的实在太粗鲁了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说阿斯顿王对这女孩开价挺高的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅甸大人的喜好也真够奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被卖掉了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女的会怎样又不关我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去告诉梵大人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊,快来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人会听见的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算人型装甲也没办法潜到水里来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会来救我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方也正尽全力搜索中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,阿斯多利亚国土辽阔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能派出去找寻区区一架人型装甲的兵力实在有限
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此就请您允许我们加入搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军一定能够找出艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们竟然会那么想得到那架人型装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以麻烦你告诉我你们如此穷追不舍的理由吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消息回报,龙已经上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳曾经救过我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次换我去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是卫兵传回来的绘图
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来可以省下搜索的工夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然没想到它会伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上派守备队过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到它已经潜入帕拉斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯,请你履行条约
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我都城的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要求寨巴哈军立刻出击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真是一位了不起的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去把迪兰度叫起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你给我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你起床速度这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那家伙出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就出现在我的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是市区
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量不要波及无辜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尽量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追到运河来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜下去,快潜下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露,你上岸去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他见识见识我们的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装甲是没办法追到水里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵跑来救我?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没受伤吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:20:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会蠢到被壁虎人给绑走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起喔,我那么蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧光光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城镇…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城镇烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.85,0:22:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这边动手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.35,0:22:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都要怪你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.89,0:22:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你在这里城镇才会烧起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你在这里我的伤□才会隐隐作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.73,0:22:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:22:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度,要是你还想继续破坏城镇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:22:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我来当你的对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连·歇萨尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.89,0:23:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.77,0:23:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.09,0:24:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.09,0:24:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.52,0:24:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.66,0:24:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使飞舞之日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:36.85,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:45.30,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.76,0:23:52.93,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:59.08,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.15,0:24:01.44,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
